        Three tiers. You earn the next one with proof, not promises.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[16px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.65] mt-5">
        Each tier unlocks more revenue, more features, more visibility, and signals to your clients that you've actually done it. Tier is assigned by us after review, not at signup.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">

