        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[13.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] mb-5">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--orange);">&#10003;</span> Highest revenue share rate (locked for life)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--orange);">&#10003;</span> Direct founder Slack channel</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--orange);">&#10003;</span> Inherits all future tier benefits as they launch</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--orange);">&#10003;</span> Listed first in the partner directory</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--orange);">&#10003;</span> Quarterly co-marketing slot with David</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="pt-4" style="border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] mb-1" style="color:var(--orange-deep);">How you earn it</div>
          <p class="text-[12.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.65]">Apply during the founding window. Pass a brief review call with David. Cohort capped at 50.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Certified Integrator -->
      <div class="card lift p-7 border-t-[3px]" style="border-top-color:var(--blue);">
        <div class="tier-badge tier-certified-badge">CI</div>
        <div class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] mb-1" style="color:var(--blue-deep);">Tier 2 &middot; Open</div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-[1.5rem] font-bold text-[var(--ink)] mb-2">Certified OTP Integrator</h3>
        <p class="text-[13.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] mb-5 leading-[1.65]">The standard active partner tier. Enough scale to deliver real results, with full program benefits.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[13.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] mb-5">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--blue);">&#10003;</span> Standard revenue share on every client</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--blue);">&#10003;</span> Co-branded client onboarding</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--blue);">&#10003;</span> Multi-tenant partner dashboard</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--blue);">&#10003;</span> Certified OTP Integrator badge</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--blue);">&#10003;</span> Partner directory listing</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="pt-4" style="border-top:1px solid var(--line);">
          <div class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] mb-1" style="color:var(--blue-deep);">How you earn it</div>
          <p class="text-[12.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] leading-[1.65]">Complete OTP certification training. Get your first paying client live for 30 consecutive days.</p>
