        <p class="text-[13.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] mb-5 leading-[1.65]">The proven track-record tier. Featured. White-labeled. Co-marketed. Reserved for partners who've shown the work.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[13.5px] text-[var(--ink-soft)] mb-5">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--green);">&#10003;</span> White-label option (your brand, our protocol)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--green);">&#10003;</span> Featured partner status on orgtp.com</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--green);">&#10003;</span> Co-marketing campaigns with OTP</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="flex-shrink-0" style="color:var(--green);">&#10003;</span> Early access to new features and agent runtime betas</li>
