        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow mb-4" style="color:var(--orange-deep);">A note from the founder</div>
          <blockquote class="font-display text-[var(--ink)] leading-[1.45]"
                      style="font-size:clamp(1.2rem,2.2vw,1.6rem); font-weight:600;">
            "I built OTP because my own company hit the wall everyone is about to hit. Half my team is AI now. The org chart broke. The KPIs broke. The way we coordinate broke. I had to invent the operating layer to fix it. The trusted advisors who get to this first, the EOS implementers, the fractional CXOs, the AI consultancies, have a window right now. I'd rather be in business with people I respect than chase scale alone."
          </blockquote>
